ests on the basis of the conceptual and logical reality of human language. The book also offers an in-depth overview of the literature on layered modal constructions as well as a valuable and extensive set of analyzed data which will be of great interest for researchers interested in verbal systems, modality, and Slavic languages.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 27. Okt 2021) 4aKroatisch. 4aModalverben.  aCroatian.  aDouble modals.0 cEPUBz97831107274250 cprintz978311072731940uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311072732640uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110727326423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110727326/original  aEBA_CL_LS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_LS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK